{"tid":1382790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想分享下有個政見同自己一樣既爸爸會點","createTime":"2019-07-29T14:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T14:22:20.000Z","uid":260077,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"736ff40390f1b8b7e9afe2d0b80937e6678be8ba","tid":1382790,"uid":260077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:22:20.000Z","msg":"發夢立會上水沙田⋯⋯爸爸都係叫我小心啲，又報下live直播消息比我知<br />\n<br />\n直到元朗係wts收到<br />\n<br />\n「保護自己，買2罐可樂+一個布做環保袋。」<br />\n「還拖」<br />\n「兩樣嘢 帶喺身邊 都唔會犯法， 用個環保袋入住兩3罐汽水有人衝埋嚟兜頭打佢， 啱啱諗到」<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n有啲過晒火既都唔講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部都係我爸send黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我爸每次發完夢都會屌尻我唔夠勇/冇戰術/比啲散水狗嗌散晒（元朗個日翻到屋企比佢屌左一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n但佢每次都會支持我去發夢，話係我人生既歷練<br />\n<br />\n佢又會教我唔同既方法自保/幫其他人（曾經投稿老豆搵仔 tg <a href=\"https://t.me/Dadfindboy）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDadfindboy%EF%BC%89&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiSEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=07ec04b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Dadfindboy）</a><br />\n<br />\n重分享防具製作方法比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得有呢個爸爸係我一世人遇到最好既事<br />\n<br />\n爸爸我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知你有睇連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望你睇到<br />\n<br />\n利申絲，爸爸係世界上最好既男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望巴絲打睇完知道父母輩裡面都係有人支持我地㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}